{"tid":2176542,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【好得意咩】黃心美任由半歲姨甥女狂踢愛犬：Muffin係超犯賤㗎","createTime":"2020-08-27T07:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T13:12:22.000Z","uid":42411,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4ac331c35be04bd3286e23abed2e3825eaa53e","tid":2176542,"uid":42411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHuD5wc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHuD5wc.png&h=ebad085a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃心美和黃心穎兩姊妹，向來痛錫姨甥女「豆豆」，從二人在IG鋪天蓋地po同BB玩的照片便知。兩姊妹當BB是寶，她們平時亦表現到是愛狗之人，黃心穎早前領養一隻唐狗，而黃心美本身則飼養了4隻魔天使。<br />\n<br />\n養狗經驗豐富的她，經常在鏡頭前和狗狗又攬又錫，不過昨晚她在IG story上載的幾條短片，卻令不少狗主睇到有點火滾。黃心美所po的3條短片中，其中一條是「豆豆」用雙腳狂撐魔天使Muffin，撐了幾吓後，Muffin終於頂唔順，起身走去另一邊。<br />\n<br />\n至於另外兩條片，「豆豆」則用手扯狗狗條尾和抆牠的毛，拍片的黃心美不但沒有阻止姨甥女，還竟然留言說：「Muffin係超犯賤㗎！」、「堅係犯賤㗎！」、「Muffin犯賤嘅底可以話係根深蒂固！」估計她所表達的意思是，即使被BB又扯毛又抆尾，Muffin都沒有反抗，所以覺得牠有點犯賤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200827/7ENJA55QNFDTJG3UGCH4CK7BSI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200827%2F7ENJA55QNFDTJG3UGCH4CK7BSI%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=79fe81e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200827%2F7ENJA55QNFDTJG3UGCH4CK7BSI%2F&h=52c04dff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200827/7ENJA55QNFDTJG3UGCH4CK7BSI/</a>"},{"pid":"75ba5af8706fe06e7f1473ead69456a262a97d0c","tid":2176542,"uid":228894,"like":17,"dislike":9,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:07:39.000Z","msg":"黃心美<br />\n美心黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美心黃即係silly 癡線冇可以會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a121a0791150c77a7d58cfa958a416a9918532e","tid":2176542,"uid":261172,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"呢D冇智商既肉便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ce673a1c476744adf7807dcbed2702b98a022f","tid":2176542,"uid":15644,"like":19,"dislike":5,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:09:29.000Z","msg":"Bb 係咁架啦<br />\n踢得死隻狗咩on9咁都係新聞"},{"pid":"b089a9d8abb6564685a80fd3610a33b9c594f332","tid":2176542,"uid":370705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75ba5af8706fe06e7f1473ead69456a262a97d0c","tid":2176542,"uid":228894,"like":17,"dislike":9,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:07:39.000Z","msg":"黃心美<br />\n美心黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美心黃即係silly 癡線冇可以會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d33bf060b9634a802545341a299dc6bd2bf2609","tid":2176542,"uid"